## Comparative Summary of Pros and Cons

| Aspect                    | Positive Effects                                            | Negative Effects                                              |
|---------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Social Connection**     | Enables global communication; supports introverts; reduces isolation | Can replace real interactions; leads to loneliness and anxiety |
| **Mental Health**         | Provides support groups; promotes coping during crises      | Increases depression, anxiety, body image issues             |
| **Information Access**    | Rapid dissemination of news and health info; civic engagement | Spread of misinformation and manipulation                     |
| **Self-Image**            | Platforms for self-expression and identity exploration      | Promotes unrealistic comparisons; worsens self-esteem       |
| **Communication**         | Facilitates social skills development for some              | Cyberbullying; miscommunication due to lack of cues          |
| **Time Management**       | Enables flexible communication and learning                 | Addiction; time wasted; reduced productivity                  |
| **Professional Use**      | Job networking and marketing opportunities                   | Commercialization can distort authentic interactions          |

